{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "afd52ac6-44a8-409e-9583-3d62d59bc76a", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/afd52ac6-44a8-409e-9583-3d62d59bc76a@4.pkg/1772602169333/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602169476", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/afd52ac6-44a8-409e-9583-3d62d59bc76a@4.pkg/1772602169333/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772602169476"}, "identifier": "afd52ac6-44a8-409e-9583-3d62d59bc76a", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #auto;\">天黑了，天黑了，为什么还不回家？（如果）不是为了君主，何必还在露水中劳作！</span><span style=\"color: #auto;\"><br />&#x200e;</span><span style=\"color: #auto;\">天黑了，天黑了，为什么还不回家？（如果）不是为了养活你们，何必还在泥浆中劳作！</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: #auto;\">A.</span><span>两首诗在句式和用韵上都比较自由，均属于古体诗。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B.《式微》通过咏叹的方式、质问的语气，直接抒情。&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D.乙无描写。</span></p></div>"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>阅读选文，回答相关问题。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>甲 &nbsp;石壕吏 &nbsp;杜甫</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.29in; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background:#FFFFFF\">暮投石壕村，有吏夜捉人。老翁逾墙走，老妇出门看。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.29in; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background:#FFFFFF\">​</span><span style=\"background:#FFFFFF\">‎</span><span style=\"background:#FFFFFF\">吏呼一何怒，妇啼一何苦！听妇前致词：三男邺城戍。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.29in; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background:#FFFFFF\">一男附书至，二男新战死。存者且偷生，死者长已矣！</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.29in; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background:#FFFFFF\">室中更无人，惟有乳下孙。有孙母未去，出入无完裙。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left: 0.29in; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"background:#FFFFFF\">老妪力虽衰，请从吏夜归。急应河阳役，犹得备晨炊。</span><br />\n<span style=\"background:#FFFFFF\">‎</span><span style=\"background:#FFFFFF\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;夜久语声绝，如闻泣幽咽。天明登前途，独与老翁别。</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>乙 &nbsp;式微《诗经》</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>式微，式微，胡不归?微君之故，胡为乎中露?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span>式微，式微，胡不归?微君之躬，胡为乎泥中?</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>下列理解正确的一项是( &nbsp; )</span></p>\n</div>\n", "label": "", "title": "阅读选文，回答相关问题。甲  石壕吏  杜甫暮投石壕村，有吏夜捉人。老翁逾墙走，老妇出门看。‎吏呼一何怒，妇啼一何苦！听妇前致词：三男邺城戍。一男附书至，二男新战死。存者且偷生，死者长已矣！室中更无人，惟有乳下孙。有孙母未去，出入无完裙。老妪力虽衰，请从吏夜归。急应河阳役，犹得备晨炊。‎    夜久语声绝，如闻泣幽咽。天明登前途，独与老翁别。乙  式微《诗经》式微，式微，胡不归?微君之故，胡为乎中", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/afd52ac6-44a8-409e-9583-3d62d59bc76a@4.pkg/item.json?v=1747212628741", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify